# Experiment 2: ML Scoring Evaluation
# All SNDlib instances with default + 3 ML configurations
# Format: <network_file>;<settings_file>

# Settings configurations:
# 1. default.toml - baseline with full ML weight (100%)
# 2. benders_ML-0.7-5C-20S-5R.toml -    ML Score 0.7,   5 cuts max, 20 stabilization, 5 root stabilization
# 3. benders_ML-0.7-10C-20S-5R.toml -   ML Score 0.7,  10 cuts max, 20 stabilization, 5 root stabilization
# 4. benders_ML-0.5-20S.toml -          ML Score 0.7,               20 stabilization
# 5. benders_ML-0.5-5C-20S-5R.toml -    ML Score 0.5,   5 cuts max, 20 stabilization, 5 root stabilization
# 6. benders_ML-0.5-10C-20S-5R.toml -   ML Score 0.5,  10 cuts max, 20 stabilization, 5 root stabilization
# 7. benders_ML-0.5-20S.toml -          ML Score 0.5,               20 stabilization
# 8. benders_ML-5C-20S.toml -                           5 cuts max, 20 stabilization
# 9. benders_ML-10C-20S.toml -                         10 cuts max, 20 stabilization

